<p style="mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt">Hinweis zur Entsorgung von Altbatterien</span></p>
<p style="mso-layout-grid-align: none" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 9pt">Der
